        <h2 class="section-title">Visits to museums</h2>
        <p>The educational visit continued with visits to two emblematic museums:</p>

        <h3>Istanbul Museum for the History of Science and Technology in the Islamic World</h3>
        <p>Students worked on specific tasks related to:</p>
        <ul class="bullets">
          <li>Astronomy and time measurement</li>
          <li>Mathematics and Engineering</li>
          <li>Medicine and biology</li>
          <li>Optics and Physics</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Rahmi Koç Museum</h3>
        <p>Students explored:</p>
        <ul class="bullets">
          <li>Innovations in transportation</li>
          <li>Marine Engineering</li>
          <li>Advances in aviation</li>
          <li>Communication devices and scientific instruments</li>
        </ul>

        <p>This mobility has become an unforgettable experience, filled with new knowledge, practical experience and valuable international friendships. We thank all participants, organizers and partner schools for the inspiring cooperation!</p>

